《'''奧斯卡的一天'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Fruitvale Station'''''}}）是一部2013年美国[[傳記电影|傳記电影]]，由[[瑞恩·库格勒|瑞恩·库格勒]]编剧并执导，是他第一部擔任導演的電影，根据{{link-en|奧斯卡·格蘭特命案|Shooting of Oscar Grant}}的真实历史事件改编而成<ref name="HR">{{cite web|last=Fleming|first=Mike|title=Sundance: The Weinstein Company Acquires ‘Fruitvale’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/fruitvale-sundance-film-festival-dea-weinstein/|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=2013-01-26|date=January 21, 2013|archive-date=2013-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227050304/http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/fruitvale-sundance-film-festival-dea-weinstein/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=LAT>{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-sundance-2013-fruitvale-wins-grand-jury-prize-20130126,0,5342255.story |title=Sundance 2013: 'Fruitvale' wins Grand Jury Prize |first=Julie |last=Makinen |newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=January 26, 2013 |accessdate=2013-01-26 |archive-date=2013-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525053941/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-sundance-2013-fruitvale-wins-grand-jury-prize-20130126,0,5342255.story |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{cite news |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117949029/ |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |title=Fruitvale |first=Geoff |last=Berkshire |date=January 20, 2013 |accessdate=2013-01-27 |archive-date=2013-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130209021014/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117949029/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

本片獲得了2013年[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]评审团大奖、观众奖，以及[[第66届戛纳电影节|第66届戛纳电影节]][[一種注目|一種注目]]单元未来奖<ref name=LAT/><ref name="Cannes2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/59652.html|title=2013 Official Selection|date=18 April 2013|accessdate=18 April 2013|work=Cannes|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211120304/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/59652.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="HWR-UCR">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-missing-picture-wins-regard-558551|title=Cannes: 'The Missing Picture' Wins Un Certain Regard Prize|date=26 May 2013|accessdate=26 May 2013|work=Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528150056/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-missing-picture-wins-regard-558551|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国于2013年7月12日上映<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/films.php?id=99154 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2014-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330224043/http://www.comingsoon.net/films.php?id=99154 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==剧情==
改編自真實事件，22歲黑人男子奧斯卡·格蘭特（Oscar Grant）于2009年[[新年|新年]]狂歡後，自[[舊金山|舊金山]]返家途中於[[舊金山灣區捷運系統|舊金山灣區捷運]]列車上與人發生衝突，爾後在福祿維爾車站月台被捷運警察拘留上銬時，遭到其中一名白人警察Johannes Mehserle槍殺（據其發言是誤將[[手槍|手槍]]當作[[泰瑟|泰瑟槍]]使用）。奧斯卡·格蘭特於送醫七小時後過世，因而引起美國社会很大的反响。

